HEADWORD: Envermeil
<hw>En*ver"meil</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <ety>[Pref.
<ets>en-</ets> + <ets>vermeil</ets>: cf. OF. <ets>envermeiller</ets>.
See <er>Vermil</er>.]</ety> <def>To color with, or as with, vermilion;
